               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 13ra-61ra)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 13ra-17va)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols.17vb-19ra) &#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki… “I worship Thee …” (fols. 19ra-21ra) &#xD; I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām
                     "Miracles of Mary": 33 miracles (fols. 21ra-61ra)&#xD; II) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 15 miracles (fols. 61rb-86vb)&#xD; III) Excerpts from the
                     book of the Old and New Testaments and the missal (?)(fols. 87r-93r)&#xD; &#xD;
                     Additiones 1-4.</summary>
